response.overview: "SB2: Da Kiennan" from the FrontSide Films series. It's the second video in the series, following "SB1: A Skiboarding Journey". The video showcases various skiboarding locations and contests, including the Winter X Games, US Freeskiing Open, and events in Austria, France, Japan, and Canada. It features established riders like Neal Lyons, Mick Nick, and Bryce Raney, along with new talent pushing the sport's boundaries.
response.title: SB2: Da Kiennan
